latestIgtvVideos.title: And Still I Rise - Maya Angelou
latestIgtvVideos.caption: This isn’t just now, it’s our history and life. And in times where there is darkness. I turn to past and present leaders who offer words of strength. I hope that Maya Angelou’s voice can give some comfort for my black brothers and sisters. Who are feeling emotionally and physically tired from this forever ongoing fight for justice overseas and in my homeland Australia. ——— I will be sharing and cheering more melenated and Indigenous Australian voices for us to learn from 🖤 Right now you can visit my BLM highlight to engage more in the discussion 🖤
